headline: Date Set For Moody's Earnings Release And Investor Teleconference
summary: NEW YORK, April 08, 2025--Moody's Corporation (NYSE: MCO) will release its first quarter 2025 results before the start of NYSE trading on Tuesday, April 22, 2025. A copy of the earnings release and supplemental presentation slides will be posted on Moody's Investor Relations website, ir.moodys.com.
